OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FA father-of-two who took his toddler
OL,7,Fto a riot has been jailed.
OL,9,FMason Reddy, 24, was seen throwing
OL,10,Fbricks and rocks at a hotel housing
OL,11,Fasylum seekers in Rotherham, while
OL,12,Fshouting threats.
OL,14,FHe was also witnessed throwing
OL,15,Fmissiles at officers, hitting out at
OL,16,Friot shields and cheering rioters who
OL,17,Fwere lighting a fire at the Holiday
OL,18,FInn Express in Manvers during the
OL,19,Fincident on 4 August.
