OL,3,CDad who took two-year-old son to riot
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FA journalist also said they saw Reddy
OL,7,Fshouting a racial slur while carrying
OL,8,Fa boy aged around two in his arms.
OL,10,FFootage showed him holding the boy
OL,11,Fwhile walking in front of a line of
OL,12,Friot police as a fire burned in the
OL,13,Fbackground.
OL,15,FFive officers identified Reddy, from
OL,16,FBarnsley, by his "distinctive
OL,17,Fclothing", odd shoes and the fact that
OL,18,Fhe had a child and pram with him,
OL,19,FSheffield Crown Court heard.
