OL,3,CDad who took two-year-old son to riot
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FIn mitigation, the court heard Reddy,
OL,7,Fwho has no previous convictions, had
OL,8,Ftaken his son with him as he was
OL,9,Fintending to protest peacefully.
OL,11,FHe admitted violent disorder and was
OL,12,Fjailed for three years.
OL,14,FAlso jailed on Thursday was a man
OL,15,Fwhose son had already been sentenced
OL,16,Ffor his part in the riot.
