OL,3,CDad who took two-year-old son to riot
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FStephen Roughley, 44, was locked up
OL,7,Ffor two years and eight months after
OL,8,Fadmitting violent disorder. His son
OL,9,FKenzie Roughley, 18, became the first
OL,10,Fperson to be sentenced over the
OL,11,FRotherham disorder last month.
OL,13,FSheffield Crown Court heard Stephen
OL,14,FRoughley, from Pontefract, initiated
OL,15,Fchants of "get them out" and made
OL,16,F"disparaging remarks of a sexual
OL,17,Fnature to police officers" before
OL,18,Fthrowing a missile at a police van.
