OL,6,FAnother man, who grabbed and pushed
OL,7,Friot shields while at the front of a
OL,8,Fmob, was jailed for two years.
OL,10,FRegan Urruty Dever, 22, of Doncaster,
OL,11,Fwas only there for 20 minutes and had
OL,12,Fbeen to Tesco and for a katsu curry
OL,13,Fbeforehand.
OL,15,FDaniel Dicks, 33, of Goldthorpe, who
OL,16,Fpushed a shopping trolley into the
OL,17,Fpath of a police van, ripped up fence
OL,18,Fposts to be used as missiles and was
OL,19,Fpart of a crowd chanting racist
OL,20,Fremarks was jailed for two years and
OL,21,Feight months.
